{"tid":746020,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"23歲男堅持不願洗澡 還想跳樓「以死明志」","createTime":"2018-07-17T08:46:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T08:55:51.000Z","uid":75969,"like":3,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"96a5d5491c1437ccca74fb7f99baa04357cdf22c","tid":746020,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:46:35.000Z","msg":"大陸安徽省安慶市一位男子，在11日因為不想洗澡與母親發生衝突，一怒之下爬到自家三樓樓頂揚言跳樓。家人通報警方後，消防隊和警力到現場進行救援，結果雙方僵持近1個小時，最後警方和消防員只好一擁而上將他上銬，再將男子搬離屋頂。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ebcnews.s3.amazonaws.com/images/2018/07/16/15317508129327ZdvS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Febcnews.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2F2018%2F07%2F16%2F15317508129327ZdvS.jpg&h=69f927bb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://ebcnews.s3.amazonaws.com/images/2018/07/16/15317508287569TLL4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Febcnews.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2F2018%2F07%2F16%2F15317508287569TLL4.jpg&h=9d24a794&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n男子母親接受警方調查時說:「他不洗澡，這個大熱天他不洗澡，他不洗澡」警方問到：「所以你就逼他洗澡？」母親回說：「我叫他洗澡還是不出聲還是不洗澡。」而當警方問：「他23歲還沒有工作嗎？」母親則答道：「他有事不做，他懶嘛！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ebcnews.s3.amazonaws.com/images/2018/07/16/15317508560432SAcx.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Febcnews.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2F2018%2F07%2F16%2F15317508560432SAcx.jpg&h=0838d0e6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n被問到男子為何鬧自殺，他的母親向警方供稱，只因為他不想洗澡。「這個大熱天不洗澡，他不洗澡&hellip;」。當地媒體指，消防員把男子抬回屋內後，讓他冷靜下來，男子最後同意好好的與母親溝通，討論是否洗澡。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://ebcnews.s3.amazonaws.com/images/2018/07/16/15317508793627zLuz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Febcnews.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fimages%2F2018%2F07%2F16%2F15317508793627zLuz.jpg&h=7218213e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ebc.net.tw/news.php?nid=121164\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ebc.net.tw%2Fnews.php%3Fnid%3D121164&d=dY1SNdcIbrVQgb7bjg36EW6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=187393f3\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.ebc.net.tw/news.php?nid=121164</a>"},{"pid":"e172430d697ac203857a0713d5ec8c21dc1dfb45","tid":746020,"uid":21423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:50:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6b36ff978653c5f179ab14c8039bd9897fe23aab","tid":746020,"uid":49136,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:52:55.000Z","msg":"男子最後同意好好的與母親溝通，討論是否洗澡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30d6706ec0f198f177d85604f9498dcc2cdc1e21","tid":746020,"uid":95,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:55:11.000Z","msg":"支那寧捨多怪人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6701e0176964ff82fd95b1f9455a177fcddde909","tid":746020,"uid":41243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-17T08:55:51.000Z","msg":"當自己Rasputin?"}]}